==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Renning
<hw>Ren"ning</hw> <pr>(r?n"n?ng)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>See 2d
<er>Rennet</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Asses' milk is holden for to be thickest, and therefore they use
it instead of <qex>renning</qex>, to turn milk.</q>
<rj><qau>Holland.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Renomee</ent>⟦br⟧
